whole_object: In a world where signs are merely suggestions, one man takes a stand—by not using the pedestrian walkway.
single_object:
- Building: This building is so popular, even the stairs are spiraling out of control.
- Workers: The workers keep erecting stories about their construction skills, but they're all built on solid foundations.
- Truck: Despite many hauls, this truck never tires of its job, always staying wheel-y committed.
- Fence: The fence is the ultimate gossip—it’s been around the block, seen it all, and still keeps things separated.
- Sign: This sign is so demanding, it gives walking directions one foot at a time.
- Boxes: The boxes lead a very squared existence, always thinking inside the box.
- Tree: The tree stands so quietly, you'd think it was practicing 'bark' meditation.
- Pallet: This pallet aspired to be an artist but found it couldn't handle the pressure of the palette.
